data.description: Expansive 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom Ranch home nestled on a tranquil cul-de-sac street, offering a generous 1.27-acre lot within the Pleasant Valley School District. Upon entering, you'll be embraced by the warmth of the sun-filled living room, an inviting dining area, and an open kitchen with breakfast seating. Further, the heart of this home lies in the generously sized family room, which also doubles as a sunroom, basking in an abundance of natural light and stunning views of the serene surroundings. As you venture down the hall, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms, a main full bathroom, and at the end of the corridor, a private sanctuary awaits: the primary bedroom suite. This retreat features a full bath with a jetted tub, a separate shower stall, a spacious walk-in closet, and the added convenience of direct access to the laundry room – making laundry day a breeze. Partially finished basement is accented with a cozy pellet stove and convenient access to a two-car garage. Additionally, there's an extra 1-car garage space that could serve as a workshop or provide valuable storage options. Step outside, and you'll find your own private oasis, complete with an in-ground pool, perfect for creating unforgettable memories with friends and family. With endless potential and value, this home can become your forever haven with a personal touch! Property is being sold as-is.  Call today!
